    <title>About option sets</title>
    <para>Option sets provide a pre-defined drop-down (enumerated) list for use in DHIS2. You can
        define any kind of options.</para>
    <example>
        <para>An option set called &quot;Delivery type&quot; would have the options:
            &quot;Normal&quot;, &quot;Breach&quot;, &quot;Caesarian&quot; and
            &quot;Assisted&quot;.</para>
    </example>
